pageContext.claim: “Secretary Acosta, who has created some incredible healthcare programs, cooperative programs, where the price of healthcare has really gone down, much far below Obamacare. Far below. And some really great programs that people are signing up, I hear, in tremendous numbers.”
pageContext.analysis: Association plans are cheaper because they provide fewer benefits and protections. By definition, they do not provide "better health insurance" though some healthier Americans might prefer to have a skimpier option.
